column5: Just got a phone call from Bly...she said that by 730ish, a few fish had already been caught.....  Here I am at the office...hmmmm...something is wrong here.... LOL
Wait a minute...it should say expect a huge Walleye report later if Bly is on the water  Tony
Well, the day's not over yet....with her you just never know!!!

Well, even though Bly's not on my team, I can't help but wish the best for her.  What a treat to get out with the "master of steel"  I guess you didn't join them cause somebody's got to earn the bacon eh Cliff  Go Carol!!!  Joey

WERE BACK!!! BUT I'LL LET BLY DO THE REPORT( IM GETTIN HATE/ENVY MAIL  LOL JK) WAS FUN EVEN IF THE ACTION SLOWED FROM THE OTHER DAYS!!! CLIFF YA NEVER TOLD ME YOU WERE A MALE ORDER GROOM ?? GOTTA DO WHAT YA GOTTA DO TO GET IN EH  LOL
hate envy mail...thats a good one!

Great...now everyone knows...jeez.  She's not allowed to go fishing with you again...LOL.  She said she had a great time out there with you and little C.  She's pretty happy that skunk if off her back...she hadn't caught anything since December!  Things should be less tense around our house again....haha.
ok ok ok enough with the suspense how many did you get?
ONLY 3 !!! 1 EACH!!! LITTLE C IN ONLY 2 MINS THERE THEN CAROL THEN ME!!! NO ONE ELSE GOT ANYTHING!!!ALL MUD NOW DUE TO SOUTH WINDS!!
